WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
BAHAMAS TO VIRGINIA.
36 FOOT S/V MAGUS, RED HULL, THREE PERSONS ON BOARD,
UNREPORTED MARSH HARBOR (26-33N 077-04W) TO
NORFOLK (36-55N 076-12W). VESSELS IN VICINITY
REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST
IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO U.S. COAST GUARD RCC MIAMI,
PHONE: 305 415 6800, E-MAIL: RCCMIAMI@USCG.MIL.
